{{Youmay|the gunsmith|[[Fassa (disambiguation)|other uses of the name]]}}
'''Fassa''' was one of the largest gunsmiths in [[Tof Soren]] on [[Ord Vaxal]]. Fassa primarily produced [[Slugthrower/Legends|slugthrowers]] due to the scarcity of materials used to make [[Blaster pistol/Legends|blaster pistols]].

